   "source": [
    "# 第4天：卷积神经网络（CNN） + 批量归一化（BatchNorm）\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🎯 学习目标\n",
    "1. 理解卷积神经网络（CNN）的基本原理\n",
    "2. 掌握批量归一化（BatchNorm）技术\n",
    "3. 实现股票图表模式识别模型\n",
    "4. 应用CNN进行技术分析图像识别\n",
    "\n",
    "## 📚 理论基础\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. 卷积神经网络（CNN）\n",
    "卷积神经网络是专门用于处理网格状数据（如图像）的神经网络。\n",
    "\n",
    "**核心组件：**\n",
    "- **卷积层（Convolutional Layer）**：提取局部特征\n",
    "- **池化层（Pooling Layer）**：降低特征图维度\n",
    "- **全连接层（Fully Connected Layer）**：进行分类\n",
    "\n",
    "**数学表示：**\n",
    "$$\n",
    "h_{i,j}^{(l)} = \\sigma\\left(\\sum_{m=0}^{M-1}\\sum_{n=0}^{N-1} w_{m,n}^{(l)} \\cdot x_{i+m,j+n}^{(l-1)} + b^{(l)}\\right)\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. 批量归一化（BatchNorm）\n",
    "批量归一化是一种加速训练和提高模型性能的技术。\n",
    "\n",
    "**工作原理：**\n",
    "1. 对每个批次的数据进行归一化\n",
    "2. 学习缩放参数γ和平移参数β\n",
    "3. 在训练和测试时使用不同的统计量\n",
    "\n",
    "**数学原理：**\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\\hat{x}_i = \\frac{x_i - \\mu_B}{\\sqrt{\\sigma_B^2 + \\epsilon}}\n",
    "$$\n",
    "$$\n",
    "y_i = \\gamma \\hat{x}_i + \\beta\n",
    "$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**优点：**\n",
    "- 加速训练收敛\n",
    "- 允许使用更高的学习率\n",
    "- 减少对初始化的依赖\n",
    "- 有一定的正则化效果\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🚀 实践实现"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 导入必要的库\n",
    "import torch\n",
    "import torch.nn as nn\n",
    "import torch.nn.functional as F\n",
    "import torch.optim as optim\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from torch.utils.data import Dataset, DataLoader\n",
    "from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler\n",
    "from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split\n",
    "import warnings\n",
    "warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\n",
    "\n",
    "# 设置随机种子\n",
    "torch.manual_seed(42)\n",
    "np.random.seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"✅ 环境准备完成\")"
   ]
